#: ../../manual/editors/preferences/lights.rst:4
msgid "Lights"
msgstr "灯光"

#: ../../manual/editors/preferences/lights.rst:8
msgid "Blender Preferences Lights section."
msgstr "Blender偏好设置灯光部分。"

#: ../../manual/editors/preferences/lights.rst:14
msgid "Studio Lights"
msgstr "棚灯"

#: ../../manual/editors/preferences/lights.rst:16
msgid ""
"*Studio Lights* are used to illuminate 3D viewport during *Solid View* "
"and will not be rendered."
msgstr "*棚灯* 用于在 *Solid View* 期间照亮3D视图，不会参与渲染。"

#: ../../manual/editors/preferences/lights.rst:18
msgid ""
"Unlike lights in the scene, the lighting direction follows the viewport "
"orientation."
msgstr "与场景中的灯光不同，灯光方向是沿着视图方向的。"

#: ../../manual/editors/preferences/lights.rst:24
msgid "Editor"
msgstr "编辑器"

#: ../../manual/editors/preferences/lights.rst:26
msgid "There are up to four virtual light sources."
msgstr "最多有四个虚拟光源。"

#: ../../manual/editors/preferences/lights.rst:28
msgid ""
"The Light icons allow the user to enable or disable individual lights. At"
" least one of the four lights must remain enabled for the 3D View. The "
"lights are equal, except for their direction and color. You can control "
"the direction of the lights, as well as their diffuse and specular "
"colors."
msgstr ""
"灯光图标允许用户启用或禁用单个灯光。 必须为3D视图至少启用四个灯中的一个。 "
"除了方向和颜色外，灯光是相同的。可以控制灯光的方向，以及漫反射和镜面反射颜色。"

#: ../../manual/editors/preferences/lights.rst:46
msgid "Light"
msgstr "灯光"

#: ../../manual/editors/preferences/lights.rst:34
msgid "Use Light"
msgstr "使用灯光"

#: ../../manual/editors/preferences/lights.rst:35
msgid "Toggles the specific light."
msgstr "切换特定灯光。"

#: ../../manual/editors/preferences/lights.rst:36
msgid "Diffuse"
msgstr "漫反射"

#: ../../manual/editors/preferences/lights.rst:37
msgid "This is the constant color of the light."
msgstr "这是光的恒定颜色。"

#: ../../manual/editors/preferences/lights.rst:38
msgid "Specular"
msgstr "镜面反射"

#: ../../manual/editors/preferences/lights.rst:39
msgid "This is the highlight color of the light."
msgstr "这是灯光的高亮颜色。"

#: ../../manual/editors/preferences/lights.rst:42
msgid "Smooth"
msgstr "平滑"

#: ../../manual/editors/preferences/lights.rst:41
msgid "Smooth the shading from this light."
msgstr "从灯光中平滑阴影。"

#: ../../manual/editors/preferences/lights.rst:43
msgid "*This has the effect of lighting to be less direct.*"
msgstr "*这种照明效果不那么直接。*"

#: ../../manual/editors/preferences/lights.rst:46
msgid "Direction"
msgstr "方向"

#: ../../manual/editors/preferences/lights.rst:45
msgid "The direction of the light, (see :ref:`ui-direction-button`)."
msgstr "光的方向(参见 :ref:`ui-direction-button`)。"

#: ../../manual/editors/preferences/lights.rst:47
msgid ""
"The direction of the light will be the same as shown at the sphere "
"surface."
msgstr "光线的方向将与球体表面所示的方向相同。"

#: ../../manual/editors/preferences/lights.rst:50
msgid "Ambient Color"
msgstr "环境色"

#: ../../manual/editors/preferences/lights.rst:49
msgid "The color of unlit areas."
msgstr "未照亮区域的颜色。"

#: ../../manual/editors/preferences/lights.rst:55
msgid "MatCaps"
msgstr "快照材质"

#: ../../manual/editors/preferences/lights.rst:57
msgid ""
"This panel manages :term:`MatCap` image files which can used to light the"
" view when :ref:`MatCap <render-workbench-matcap>` shading is enabled."
msgstr ""
"此面板管理 :term:`MatCap` 图像文件，当启用 :ref:`快照材质 <render-workbench-matcap>` "
"着色时，该文件可用于照亮视图。"

#: ../../manual/editors/preferences/lights.rst:60
msgid ""
"Two kinds of images are supported for MatCaps. Regular image files and "
"multilayered OpenEXR files. When using multilayered OpenEXR files, the "
"layer named \"diffuse\" will be used as a diffuse pass, the layer named "
"\"specular\" will be used as a specular pass. Regular images will be "
"handled as \"diffuse\" and will not support specular highlighting."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/preferences/lights.rst:66
msgid ""
"The diffuse pass is multiplied with the base color of the objects and the"
" specular pass is added on top. Matcaps, that only have a diffuse pass "
"tend to look very metallic, with a separate specular pass it is possible "
"to simulate more varities of materials."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/preferences/lights.rst:72
msgid "LookDev HDRIs"
msgstr "视觉预览HDRI"

#: ../../manual/editors/preferences/lights.rst:74
msgid ""
"This panel manages :term:`HDRI` image files which can used to light the "
"view when :ref:`LookDev <3dview-lookdev>` shading is enabled."
msgstr "此面板管理 :term:`HDRI` 图像文件，当启用 :ref:`视觉预览 <3dview-lookdev>` 着色时，该文件可用于照亮视图。"

